# VEHICLE::SET_CAR_BOOT_OPEN

## Summary
Opens a car boot

## Parameters
* **VEHICLE_INDEX** vehicle

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Initially used in Max Payne 3, that's why we know the name.
